title: Hendrick Motorsports drivers struggle at Charlotte
text: Photo: Jim Topper, AP Dale Earnhardt Jr (88) hits the wall in Turn 2 during the NASCAR Sprint Cup series auto race at Charlotte Motor Speedway in Concord, N.C., Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015. (AP) — Hendrick Motorsports' struggles this season carried over to Charlotte Motor Speedway on the Sunday in a key race in the Chase for the Sprint Cup.
